## Demo Script (3-Minute Hackathon Pitch)

```
0:00 — Landing page loads with Spline 3D robot. "Trinetra: 14 AI agents 
       for credit appraisal, powered by Actian VectorAI."

0:20 — Click "Start Analysis" → Data Ingestor page. Upload a sample PDF.
       "Watch as our Doc Intelligence Agent OCRs this PDF, chunks it into 
       500-char segments, and embeds every chunk into Actian VectorAI."

0:45 — Switch to Agent Pipeline page. Show nodes lighting up in real-time.
       "14 agents process simultaneously. Every agent reads from AND writes 
       to Actian VectorAI. This isn't just storage — it's the intelligent 
       data layer."

1:15 — Switch to VectorAI Explorer. Type "fraud textile" in search.
       "Watch — I can semantically search across ALL 14 collections. News 
       articles, litigation records, RBI circulars, risk decisions — all 
       queryable with natural language."

1:45 — Toggle Hybrid Search. Add filter: phase=compliance.
       "Actian's hybrid search lets us combine vector similarity with SQL 
       filters. No other vector DB gives us this out of the box."

2:15 — Switch to Research Agent page. Show SHAP values, risk score, 
       rejection reasons.
       "Every data point in this analysis was retrieved from Actian. The 
       evidence citations? Document chunks from Actian. Similar past 
       cases? Vector search in Actian."

2:45 — Switch to Recommendation Engine. Show the CAM report.
       "A complete Credit Appraisal Memo, generated without any LLM 
       hallucination, with every claim backed by Actian-sourced evidence."

3:00 — End. "14 agents. 14 collections. One intelligent data layer. 
       Actian VectorAI."
```

