## Verification Plan

### Automated
```bash
# 1. Start VectorAI
docker-compose -f docker-compose.vectorai.yml up -d

# 2. Seed collections
cd agents && python3 seed_vectorai.py

# 3. Start backend
cd backend && python3 main.py

# 4. Seed demo application
python3 backend/seed_demo.py

# 5. Start frontend
cd Frontend/Trinetra-Intelligent-credit && npm run dev

# 6. Verify endpoints
curl http://localhost:8000/api/vectorai/collections
curl "http://localhost:8000/api/vectorai/search?q=fraud&collection=news_articles"
```

### Manual (Browser)
1. Open `http://localhost:5173`
2. Navigate to `/vectorai` — verify 14 collection cards render, search returns results
3. Navigate to `/pipeline` — verify agent nodes render with correct topology
4. Navigate to `/ingestor` — upload a PDF, verify agents start processing
5. Watch `/pipeline` update in real-time as agents complete
